descriptionHTML:
Turn your inspiration into money with EyeEm
Join a community of over 20 million creators around the globe. Gain exposure, share your inspiration, and sell your pictures—all in one place.

Up your photography game, and connect with the world’s leading brands, image buyers and media outlets. Use EyeEm Selects, a world-leading technology, to find your best shots and maximize your visibility.

There are so many ways to get discovered with EyeEm. With daily and weekly highlights from new and upcoming photographers, as well as exhibitions, awards and direct exposure to image buyers all over the world.

Get discovered and win prizes with EyeEm Missions. Let your talent shine, and submit your pictures for use by media agencies and brands such as Apple Music, Converse, Spotify and Canon.

Up your photography game, and download EyeEm today!

*YOUR INSPIRATION IS OUR PASSION*
MAKE MONEY – Sell your photos through the EyeEm marketplace and start making real money with your talent.
PERFECT PICTURES – Our community, technology, and tutorials help you improve every element of your photography.
COMPUTER VISION TECHNOLOGY – Use EyeEm’s world-leading aesthetic technology to discover which of your photos has the most selling potential.
SEAMLESS EDITING – Take advantage of a full suite of filters, styles and editing tools, all completely free.
LEARN FROM THE COMMUNITY – Advice, tips and contacts from the most passionate photography community in the world.
100% SAFE – Keep control of your copyright and easily select which photos you want to sell, as well as keeping your photos safe from infringement.

Tap into a whole new world of photography with EyeEm, and up your photography game.
comments: Now there is some issue with it, it doesn't suggest any keywords now. Have to add manually. Please do something.
Where did EyeEm vision go? Since the last update there are no suggested tags anymore. That was so useful.
Amazing!! Seeing an app evolve from grounds-up to a game-changer is a unique experience in itself! Love this update! Thanks for listening to us.

Please don't install this in your phone! The creator of this app should give us an explanation.  It's totally a waste of time. I think they are getting our pictures without us knowing then sell them personally... All my pictures are on market and 20+ are selected for premium. Please show us proof that pictures here are being sold... Sorry but this app this not good.
recentChanges: Introducing semantic tagging: When you upload a photo, you'll now see even more tags, as well as suggestions related to the tags you select! The more you add, the more accurate the suggestions become.
